Agar image mein 5 log hain aur aap sirf aik chahte hain:
*   **Logic:** Aap code mein `Max Confidence Filter` laga dein. Detector se aane wale sirf us box ko model ke pas bhejein jis ka detection score sab se zyada ho ya jo screen ke bilkul beech (center) mein ho.

