Darasal RTMPose-m "Semi-Single" architecture h. Agar aap bilkul hi 100% single person chahte hain:
*   **Global Context:** Aap model ke head mein aisi layers add kar sakte hain jo poori image ka global context lein (kyunki aapko ab baki logon se confusion ka khatra nahi h). Lekin RTMPose mein iski zaroorat kam hi parti h kyunki ye default mein hi kafi strong h.

